@startuml
title LowCortisol WebApp - Device Control Frontend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "Device Control Frontend Bounded Context" {
  class "Domain" as Frontend_device_control_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Application" as Frontend_device_control_Application <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Frontend_device_control_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Presentation" as Frontend_device_control_Presentation <<layer>>
}

Frontend_device_control_Presentation ..> Frontend_device_control_Application : user actions / state
Frontend_device_control_Application ..> Frontend_device_control_Domain : models and rules
Frontend_device_control_Application ..> Frontend_device_control_Infrastructure : API services / adapters
Frontend_device_control_Infrastructure ..> Frontend_device_control_Domain : resources and mappers
Frontend_device_control_Presentation ..> Frontend_device_control_Domain : view models

note bottom of Frontend_device_control_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/frontend/layers/device-control.
end note

@enduml
